text: The F.B.I. was an American crime television series. It stars Efrem Zimbalist, Jr., Philip Abbott, William Reynolds, Stephen Brooks, and Lynn Loring. It ran from September 1965 to September 1974. == Other websites == * Category:1965 television series debuts Category:1974 American television series endings Category:1960s American television series Category:1970s American television series Category:American crime television series Category:1965 establishments in the United States Category:English-language television programs
